46
00:03:31,604 --> 00:03:34,014
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh benar-benar, ini sudah sangat tua.</font>

47
00:03:34,014 --> 00:03:35,313
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingat dia?</font>

48
00:03:36,914 --> 00:03:39,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melihatnya beberapa
