<font color=#FFFF00>Ini..</font>

92
00:05:45,873 --> 00:05:47,013
<font color=#FFFF00>Benar-benar...</font>

93
00:05:49,544 --> 00:05:52,844
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia membuatku mendapatkan buku-buku ini?</font>

94
