105
00:06:26,714 --> 00:06:27,854
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sangat aneh.</font>

106
00:06:42,933 --> 00:06:46,003
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kehilangan orang tuaku
dan tumbuh bersama nenekku,</font>

107
00:06:46,563 --> 00:06:48,474
<font color=#FFFF00>jadi aku mengerti kesedihanmu.</font>

108
00:06:51,003 --> 00:06:53,914
<font color=#FFFF00>Laboratorium itu terbakar karena
hubungan arus pendek,</font>

109
00:06:53,914 --> 00:06:54,974
