110
00:06:54,974 --> 00:06:56,513
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah kesimpulannya.</font>

111
00:06:57,943 --> 00:06:59,613
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sangat sedih.</font>

112
00:07:04,453 --> 00:07:06,084
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau ingat sesuatu yang khusus...</font>

