120
00:07:30,243 --> 00:07:33,584
<font color=#FFFF00>Ku pikir aku melihat beberapa orang aneh.</font>

121
00:07:36,453 --> 00:07:37,724
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang aneh...</font>

122
