178
00:11:13,874 --> 00:11:15,034
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan aku juga</font>

179
00:11:16,103 --> 00:11:17,443
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini yang terakhir.</font>

180
00:11:20,544 --> 00:11:22,213
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau masih muda,
